{"sha": "7abe752684b9afa6aa4bf4f293c9f2e13bd38835", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0MTM2NTMxMDA6N2FiZTc1MjY4NGI5YWZhNmFhNGJmNGYyOTNjOWYyZTEzYmQzODgzNQ==", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Piotr Trojanek", "email": "trojanek@adacore.com", "date": "2018-07-17T08:05:54Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Pierre-Marie de Rodat", "email": "pmderodat@gcc.gnu.org", "date": "2018-07-17T08:05:54Z"}, "message": "[Ada] Attach the special GNATprove HEAP entity to the Standard package\n\nIn GNATprove mode we use frontend cross-references to synthesize the\nGlobal contract of subprograms with SPARK_Mode => Off and represent\na read/write via a pointer as a read/write of a special entity called\nHEAP. This entity is now attached to the Standard package, so that we can\nsafely check the Ekind of its Scope, which now happens in Scope_Within.\n\nThis only affects GNATprove, so no frontend test provided.\n\n2018-07-17  Piotr Trojanek  <trojanek@adacore.com>\n\ngcc/ada/\n\n\t* lib-xref-spark_specific.adb (Create_Heap): Attach the HEAP entity to\n\tthe Standard package.\n\nFrom-SVN: r262771", "tree": {"sha": "ed9db58a0f1c67f74a74ff679f98177ab0a0e9c4", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/trees/ed9db58a0f1c67f74a74ff679f98177ab0a0e9c4"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/commits/7abe752684b9afa6aa4bf4f293c9f2e13bd38835", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/7abe752684b9afa6aa4bf4f293c9f2e13bd38835", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/7abe752684b9afa6aa4bf4f293c9f2e13bd38835", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/7abe752684b9afa6aa4bf4f293c9f2e13bd38835/comments", "author": {"login": "ptroja", "id": 161602, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTYwMg==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/161602?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ptroja", "html_ur